data.meta_description: Harvey Tolbert Perdue was born on July  8, 1880 in Tennessee, son of Perry Washington Perdue and Martha C. Shanklin. He was married after er 1917 to Minnie Mae Alexander. He was married on December 22, 1898 to Mary Alice Brown, they had 2 children. He was married on 21 Dec1904 to Georgia Ella Powell, they had 5 children. He died on October 20, 1941 in Nashville, Davidson Co, Tennessee. This information is part of Family Tree of Michael L Canter and Kelly J Martin by Michael L Canter on Genealogy Online.
